{
  "id": "RAW_499319e1",
  "title": "今日开源（2025-10-11）：华盛顿大学开源 LLMc，令牌排名编码技术，实现自然语言文本紧凑存储与高效推理新突破",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==&mid=2247499710&idx=1&sn=b9b3633ae67cdf57295e9e426d696a27",
  "date": "2025-10-11 10:14:00",
  "author": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "siteName": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>\n   <br>\n  </p>\n  <div style=\"text-align: center;line-height: normal;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"></div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：LLMc</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"464\" data-imgfileid=\"100016057\" data-ratio=\"0.4027777777777778\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1152\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=43be0986&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkyWQB9icvSqGu9CQibicefOZf0IXxgRsOw2Ns4lEMQ2wWXsLq3lkAibaGXL8HGlhZavJPUnZFpx1IMDAA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★LLMc 是一个基于语言模型的自然语言文本压缩器，它通过对令牌的排名进行编码，而不是存储原始令牌 ID，从而实现更紧凑的存储格式。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">在推理过程中，LLM 提供了可能的下一个令牌的概率分布，LLMc 仅存储真实下一个令牌在分布中的排名，这些排名是小整数，因此编码更加紧凑。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/llmc\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/llmc</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：KAT-Dev-72B-Exp</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"642\" data-imgfileid=\"100016055\" data-ratio=\"0.5574074074074075\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1152\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5f3a45f1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkyWQB9icvSqGu9CQibicefOZf0hJcL4OAYbRiaxL6Ud760QbcVmTtAkUj6kiatibcRdb3PQFP7iabNicYpelQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★KAT-Dev-72B-Exp 是KAT-Coder模型的实验性强化学习版本，旨在通过开源发布向开发者和研究人员展示KAT-Coder大规模强化学习的技术创新。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">模型专为软件工程任务设计，重写了注意力内核并重新设计了训练引擎，以实现高效的强化学习训练，特别是在利用上下文管理的脚手架中。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/kat-dev-72b-exp\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/kat-dev-72b-exp</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️框架平台、必备工具</span></strong></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">PhysX-3D</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"482\" data-imgfileid=\"100016054\" data-ratio=\"0.41759259259259257\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1154\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=aa8720fa&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkyWQB9icvSqGu9CQibicefOZf0QrrBicsyQbeJng7lQTiaiatDZvHcD9DcLic3Qh6EELGyKlQvX0T2XDW4Eg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★PhysX-3D是一个用于物理基础的3D资产生成的项目，旨在提供一种新的端到端生成范式。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目在NeurIPS 2025会议上被选为Spotlight展示。PhysX-3D通过其独特的数据集和生成模型，能够生成具有物理属性的3D资产，适用于各种计算机视觉和图形学任务。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/physx\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/physx</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：Vision-Zero</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"374\" data-imgfileid=\"100016056\" data-ratio=\"0.32222222222222224\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1160\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=69f5060f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkyWQB9icvSqGu9CQibicefOZf02SwOMtfqNlvdIY8CnNstWaiaMibczBdZfQ2YpnLAu1KGiaZRnUUZrvFng%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Vision-Zero 是一个领域无关的框架，通过从任意图像对生成的竞争性视觉游戏实现视觉语言模型（VLM）的自我改进，其主要通过“谁是间谍”风格的游戏训练VLM，使模型在多个角色中进行战略推理和行动。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">Vision-Zero 能够从任意图像生成游戏，增强模型在不同领域的推理能力，并展示出对不同任务的强泛化能力。通过引入迭代自我博弈策略优化（Iterative-SPO），该项目在无标签数据上实现了可持续的性能提升，超越了其他基于注释的方法。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/vision-zero\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/vision-zero</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">③项目：Structured-Visuals</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.37592592592592594\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1148\" data-height=\"432\" data-imgfileid=\"100016058\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5be26006&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkyWQB9icvSqGu9CQibicefOZf0TPnUWulicAc2nSK7yDKiaJqxHwNiag95wWf6icbia5IsaDBpGDmbGY6sPicQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★该项目提供了一个名为StructBench的基准测试工具，包含丰富的训练数据和评估示例，旨在评估图像生成和编辑模型在结构化视觉（如图表、图形、数学图形、表格、拼图等）上的表现。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">通过多轮问答评估指标（如GPT-5或Qwen2.5-VL-72B），项目能够对模型的生成和编辑能力进行全面的评估。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/structured-visuals-2\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/structured-visuals-2</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🤖 Agent开发</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：SPEAR</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5231481481481481\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1150\" data-height=\"602\" data-imgfileid=\"100016059\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=80c1c178&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkyWQB9icvSqGu9CQibicefOZf0l0gDprUyxQukysD58YLCuUAicusZMr0xgA3Oxiakso9KKDrtZaE1X8Eg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★SPEAR 是一种基于课程的自我模仿学习框架，旨在训练能够处理长期、稀疏奖励任务的代理语言模型（LLM）。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该框架通过利用辅助工具奖励来鼓励广泛的技能探索，并通过自我模仿来利用成功的经验轨迹，从而在探索与利用之间实现平衡。SPEAR 的自适应课程能够稳定训练过程，提高效率，并在保持良好控制的熵的同时，扩展探索空间。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/spear\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/spear</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章汇总了包括自然语言文本压缩器 LLMc、AI 代码模型 KAT-Dev-72B-Exp、3D 资产生成项目 PhysX-3D、VLM 自我改进框架 Vision-Zero 等在内的六个最新开源 AI 项目和工具，覆盖模型、框架与 Agent 开发。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章汇总了包括自然语言文本压缩器 LLMc、AI 代码模型 KAT-Dev-72B-Exp、3D 资产生成项目 PhysX-3D、VLM 自我改进框架 Vision-Zero 等在内的六个最新开源 AI 项目和工具，覆盖模型、框架与 Agent 开发。",
  "summary": "该文章作为“今日开源”系列，精炼地介绍了六个前沿的 AI 开源项目。其中包括：华盛顿大学的 LLMc，一个通过令牌排名编码实现文本紧凑存储与高效推理的自然语言文本压缩器；KAT-Dev-72B-Exp，一个专为软件工程任务设计的 KAT-Coder 模型强化学习实验版本；PhysX-3D，一个用于物理基础的 3D 资产生成项目；Vision-Zero，一个通过竞争性视觉游戏实现 VLM 自我改进的领域无关框架；Structured-Visuals，一个评估图像生成和编辑模型在结构化视觉表现上的基准测试工具；以及 SPEAR，一个基于课程的自我模仿学习框架，用于训练处理长期、稀疏奖励任务的 Agent 语言模型。文章旨在快速呈现最新的技术突破和开源进展。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "LLMc 通过令牌排名编码，实现自然语言文本的紧凑存储与高效推理",
      "explanation": "该压缩器不存储原始令牌 ID，而是存储令牌在 LLM 生成概率分布中的排名，从而大幅减少存储空间并提高推理效率。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Vision-Zero 框架利用竞争性视觉游戏推动 VLM 自我改进，实现强泛化能力",
